de.uka.ipd.sdq.simucom.rerunsimulation.runconfig

Class GeneratedProjectChooseSimulationTab

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.debug.ui.AbstractLaunchConfigurationTab
      • de.uka.ipd.sdq.simucom.rerunsimulation.runconfig.GeneratedProjectChooseSimulationTab
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.eclipse.debug.ui.ILaunchConfigurationTab, org.eclipse.debug.ui.ILaunchConfigurationTab2

    public class GeneratedProjectChooseSimulationTab
extends org.eclipse.debug.ui.AbstractLaunchConfigurationTab
    The tab in the rerun simulation configuration that shows the generated project and its models used. Currently, all model paths have to be included in this tab since de.uka.ipd.sdq.simucom.rerunsimulation.jobs that are needed in order for the rerun simulator to work, include checking the validity of the models.
    Author:
    Michael Junker
